{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "第十八回\"杀人者死\"：小马与常无意面见狼山之王朱五太爷。朱五太爷以玲珑双剑威胁，常无意以极速快剑震慑。朱五太爷以小马朋友（张聋子、香香、蓝家兄妹）的安全为要挟，郝生意出现承认自己是出卖众人的\"猎狗\"。常无意怒杀郝生意，朱五太爷以\"杀人者死\"规矩逼小马杀常无意，小马机智反驳——郝生意自认是狗，杀狗不犯规矩。朱五太爷大笑放人，小马与朋友们在狼山虎背上继续求生。张聋子对香香的默默守护令人动容。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "只要是剑，都能伤人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "一寸长，一寸强，一寸短，一寸险。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "一柄剑是否可怕，并不在于它的长短。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "人也一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这两人都是侏儒，可是他们从十岁已练剑，现在他们已四十一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我知道他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "昔年天下第一剑客燕南天，身高一丈七寸，但是剑法之轻灵变化，当世无敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "当今最高大的剑客，号称巨无霸，他的剑法却比不上白玉京。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我知道他已败在‘长生剑’下十三次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你也应该知道，当今江湖中练剑的人，最高大的人也不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "当今江湖中练剑的人，最矮小的却无疑必是玲珑双剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你知道的倒不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "这两人就是玲珑双剑，死在他们剑下的，至今最少已有一百一十七人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "差不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他们的腰带，就是他们的剑。玲珑双剑，金银交辉，金剑长三尺七寸七，银剑长四尺一寸，人短剑长，凌空飞击，很少人能通过他们的剑下！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "的确很少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "要破他们的剑，只有一种法子！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "要他们根本无法拔出他们的剑。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "好！好快的剑！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我的拳头也不慢。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "却不知是你的拳快，还是他的剑快。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你们不想试试？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "也许我们迟早总会试—试的，可是现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "现在我只要我的朋友们安全无恙，太平过山。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他们太平过了山，你的拳头，他的剑，就都是我的？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好朋友，果然不愧是好朋友。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你们是九个上山的。三个到了太阳湖，你们在这里，还有四个人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "在一个安全之地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "那地方真的安全？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这狼山止，真正的安全之地只有一处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "太平客栈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "不是太平客栈是哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是这里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "普天之下，绝没有任何人敢在这里惹事生非，纵然丁喜和邓定侯到了这里，也绝不敢放肆无礼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "除此之外呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "除此之外，无论他们在哪里，随时都可能有杀身之祸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "现在他们究竟是否平安？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们是怎么来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是我带来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "想不到你又做了一件好生意。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这次我做的却是件赔本生意，虽然没赔钱，却赔了不少力气。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "赔本的生意你也做？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只此一次，下不为例。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他们都是我的客人，我总不能让他们糊里糊涂就死在那山洞里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "什么山洞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "飞云泉后面的一个山洞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你怎知他们在那里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这位常先生虽然觉得那地方又平安、又秘密，却不知那地方才是真正有死无生的绝地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "狼山上没有人不知道那地方，前面飞泉险洞，滑石密布，无论谁都很难从里面攻出来，后面更无路可退，若有人攻进去，你让你们往哪里走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "那么秘密的地方，你能找得到，倒也不容易。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "若不是有人带路，实在很难找得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "带路的人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "一定是猎狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "猎狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "猎人先放条狗出去把老虎引到有陷阱地方，老虎才会掉下去，这种狗，就叫做猎狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你知道那条猎狗是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "就是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我答应过那老太婆，要报她一次恩；我也答应过朱五太爷，绝对听他老人家的话，现在我两样都做到了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你们要我带你们来见朱五太爷，我已带你们来了，因为朱五太爷也正好要我带你们来见他，所以我不但还了那老太婆的情，也没有违抗朱五太爷的命令。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我是个生意人，要做生意，就得两面讨好，谁都不能得罪的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你为什么要杀柳大脚？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "要杀她的不是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只有朱五太爷才能叫我杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "柳大脚得罪了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我是个生意人，只管做生意，别的事我从来不问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "杀人也是生意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不但是生意，而且通常都是好生意。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "这种生意我也常做。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "只不过我通常只杀人，不杀狗。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这附近好像没有狗。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "有—条。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你既然从不杀狗，这次当然也不会破例。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "偶而破例一次也无妨。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你好大的胆子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他的胆子本来就不小。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你竟敢在这里杀人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他本来不敢的，只不过他也不愿坏了自己的规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "什么规矩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他一向不喜欢别人骗他，骗了他的人，从来没有活过半个时辰的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你知不知道这里的规矩？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "什么规矩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "杀人者死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "这是条好规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "所以我也不愿有人坏了这条规矩。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我也不愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那么现在你就替我杀了他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "反正我早就想试试，究竟是我的拳头快，还是你的剑快。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "快擦干你剑上的血。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "因为我若杀不了你，你就会杀了我。我不愿让一柄上面还带着狗血的剑刺入我喉咙里去，我连狗肉都不吃。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "不行，绝对不行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "什么事不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我不能杀他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "因为我忽然想起了一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "你这里的规矩，是杀人者死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他杀的却不是人，是狗。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "我想你这里总不会有‘杀狗者死’这条规矩。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们果然都不愧是好朋友，不管怎么样，我总得让你们先见上一面。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    }
